item.description:
@m.dog311 wrote:

So I checked my email for the first time in about 2 months tonight… Apparently I got accepted to this beta about 2 weeks ago.

Moparisthebest:

Ok, I have a question about these live gamertags. I got accepted into the AOE beta with the gamertag ‘moparisthebest’, but when I installed the windows live client, I had some default gamertag, and when I tried to change it to ‘moparisthebest’ it said it was already in use, but AOE won’t let you play it with anything but the one you got accepted with. So how do I change it to ‘moparisthebest’ since it is obviously mine (email is moparisthebest@hotmail.com)

If you already had moparisthebest registered, just log in with it.
